      <title>麦奎尔和拉斯里支持哈里斯，华尔街“蜂巢”被解雇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/wall-street-s-khive-takes-shape-as-mcguire-lasry-back-harris</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 正在迅速赢得金融界高层对她总统竞选的支持 - 并加入她的在线粉丝“KHive”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/wall-street-s-khive-takes-shape-as-mcguire-lasry-back-harris</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 17:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将重要会议移出匈牙利以抗议奥尔班的外交政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/eu-moves-key-meeting-out-of-hungary-to-protest-orban-s-diplomacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟外交政策负责人表示，他计划将 8 月份的欧盟外交和防长会议从布达佩斯移至布鲁塞尔，以抗议维克托·奥尔班的外交行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/eu-moves-key-meeting-out-of-hungary-to-protest-orban-s-diplomacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年大选重启，哈里斯巩固民主党支持率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/harris-cements-democratic-support-as-2024-election-is-reset</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯迅速巩固了强大民主党人对她即将参加总统竞选的支持，努力结束党内动荡并改变唐纳德·特朗普必输的选举局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/harris-cements-democratic-support-as-2024-election-is-reset</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 16:20:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉称尚未决定新任巴西央行行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lula-says-he-still-has-to-agree-on-new-brazil-central-bank-head</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦表示，他和财政部长费尔南多·阿达德仍需就新央行行长人选达成一致，投资者正在考虑这一变化是否会改变该国的货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lula-says-he-still-has-to-agree-on-new-brazil-central-bank-head</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:27:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉称马杜罗需要学习如何输掉选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lula-says-maduro-needs-to-learn-how-to-lose-an-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦警告他的长期盟友尼古拉斯·马杜罗，委内瑞拉的经济未来取决于廉洁的选举，以确保政府在国际社会面前的合法性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/lula-says-maduro-needs-to-learn-how-to-lose-an-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 15:26:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
